'''Adventure Park''' is Victoria's biggest water theme park. The park contains many attractions such as numerous [[water slide]]s and water [[playground]]s. The park was the first water park in [[Victoria, Australia|Victoria]], though has since also installed dry theme park attractions, such as a [[Spinning roller coaster|Crazy Coaster]] and a [[Ferris wheel]].

