'''Sofia Niño de Rivera''' (born November 23, 1981) is a Mexican [[stand-up comedy|stand-up comedian]] and actress. She was [[Mexico City]]'s 2016 woman of the year, as named by [[Chilango (magazine)|''Chilango'']],<ref name="theculturetrip">{{cite news|url=https://theculturetrip.com/north-america/mexico/articles/sofia-nino-de-rivera-is-mexico-citys-woman-of-the-year-heres-why/ |title=Sofía Niño De Rivera Is Mexico City's Woman Of The Year – Here’s Why |publisher=Theculturetrip.com |date=2016-12-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170319221259/https://theculturetrip.com/north-america/mexico/articles/sofia-nino-de-rivera-is-mexico-citys-woman-of-the-year-heres-why/ |archivedate=2017-03-19 |accessdate=2017-03-19}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=Redacción |url=http://www.chilango.com/agenda/evento/sofia-nino-de-rivera/ |title=Sofía Niño de Rivera |publisher=Chilango |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170319220344/http://www.chilango.com/agenda/evento/sofia-nino-de-rivera/ |archivedate=2017-03-19|accessdate=2017-03-19|language=Spanish}}</ref> and has been called a "a leading exponent of stand-up comedy in Mexico and Latin America as a whole."<ref name="theculturetrip"/>
== Career == De Rivera is a cast member on ''[[Club de Cuervos]]'', a Spanish-language [[comedy-drama]] series on [[Netflix]].<ref name="theculturetrip"/> She starred in a comedy special on the same platform titled ''Sofía Niño de Rivera: Expuesta ("Exposed")'', released on June 24, 2016.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://media.netflix.com/en/only-on-netflix/73268|title=Sofía Niño de Rivera: Expuesta|website=Netflix Media Center|language=en|access-date=2018-06-21}}</ref> She was the first woman to be given a Spanish-language Netflix comedy special.<ref name="theculturetrip"/> Her second Netflix stand-up special, Sofía Niño de Rivera: Selección Natural released on March 30, 2018.<ref>{{Citation|last=Campos|first=Raúl|title=Sofía Niño de Rivera: Selección natural|date=2018-03-30|url=https://www.imdb.com/title/tt7607378/|others=Sofia Niño de Rivera|access-date=2018-06-21|last2=Suter|first2=Jan}}</ref>
In March 2017, De Rivera appeared on a special episode of the US talk show [[Conan (talk show)|''Conan'']] titled [[Conan (talk show)#International|''Conan Without Borders: Made in Mexico'']].<ref>{{cite news|author=24 de Febrero, 2017 |url=http://www.radioformula.com.mx/notas.asp?Idn=664935&idFC=2017 |title=Sofía Niño de Rivera, en show de Conan O' Brien. Con Maxine Woodside |publisher=Radioformula.com.mx |date= |accessdate=2017-03-19|language=Spanish}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=09 de Marzo, 2017 |url=http://www.radioformula.com.mx/notas.asp?Idn=668149&idFC=2017 |title=Televisa no ha entendido cómo evolucionar: Sofía Niño de Rivera. La Taquilla, con René Franco |publisher=Radioformula.com.mx |date= |accessdate=2017-03-19|language=Spanish}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=Nidia Martínez de León |url=http://www.vanguardia.com.mx/articulo/conan-obrien-se-muda-televisa |title=Conan O’Brien ¿Se muda a Televisa? |language=Spanish |publisher=Vanguardia |date=2017-02-27 |accessdate=2017-03-19}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com.mx/2017/03/02/video-lo-que-sucedio-en-el-programa-de-conan-o-brien/ |title=VIDEO: Lo que sucedió en el programa de Conan O'Brien |publisher=Huffingtonpost.com.mx |date= |accessdate=2017-03-19|language=Spanish}}</ref>
== Personal life == De Rivera studied in Colegio Vista Hermosa, a high level school in Mexico City. De Rivera worked in advertising until she was 28, when she decided to start a new career in stand-up comedy.<ref>{{cite news|author=Andrea García Cavazos |url=https://www.entrepreneur.com/article/285151 |title=A Sofía Niño de Rivera le c*#?n los emprendedores |publisher=Entrepreneur.com |date=2016-02-29 |accessdate=2017-03-19|language=Spanish}}</ref> She was influenced by what she saw as heavy bureaucracy and her dislike of how the advertising industry does business.<ref>{{cite news|author=Nidia Martínez de León |url=http://www.vanguardia.com.mx/articulo/sofia-nino-de-rivera-pondra-reir-los-saltillenses |title=Sofía Niño de Rivera: Pondrá a reír a los saltillenses |language=Spanish |publisher=Vanguardia |date=2016-10-06 |accessdate=2017-03-19}}</ref>
